responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "3E5BBA6E4E080B5ECC2339A2B6B1F18B", "The rumble of hooves, but not those of beasts of burden. They are the firey stomping of minotaurs. I sense them. I have warned the guards, alas, they do not trust my senses over theirs. What a pity. ")
